Package org.dataconservancy.cos.rdf.support

Provides enumerations of supported OWL properties, OWL classes, relevant RDF constants, and default transformers for OWL annotations.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotatedElementPair
    Links an annotated element with an annotation on that element.
    IdentityTransform<T>

    OwlAnnotationProcessor
    Provides utility methods for processing OWL annotations.
    Rdf
    Maintains constants relating to the use of RDF.
    Rdf.Ns
    Common RDF namespaces and namespace prefixes.
